 √[3]{12} × √[3]{20} × √[3]{15} × √[3]{60} = √[3]{12 × 20 × 15 × 60}

Now, simplify the expression inside the radical:

√[3]{12 × 20 × 15 × 60} = √[3]{216000}

Finally, find the cube root of 216000:

√[3]{216000} = 60

